title: KMS12_sc: HMCL_control
treatment_protocol_ch1: RNA from RPMI-8226, KMS12-BM, and HEK-293T cell lines knocked-down with a scrambled or hDIS3 sh4 was collected 72 hours after infection.
growth_protocol_ch1: RPMI-8226 and KMS12-BM cells were cultured in RPMI medium with 10% FBS and 1% of Penicillin and Streptomycin.
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted from cells using TRIzol庐 RNA Isolation Reagent
label_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was processed using the FlashTag labeling kit, which uses a tailing reaction followed by ligation of the biotinylated signal molecule to the target RNA sample.
hyb_protocol: The labelled RNA was then hybridized to Affymetrix GeneChip庐 microRNA arrays v1.0 following Affymetrix recommended protocol.
scan_protocol: Genechips were scanned on an Affymetrix GeneChip 3000 7G scanner.
description: Global miRNA expression profiling data of KMS12-BM infected with a scrambled shRNA.
data_processing: The data were extracted using Affymetrix miRNA QC tool software (Affymetrix Inc., Santa Clara, CA, USA) using default analysis settings for normalization and summarization methods.
contact_department: Department of Oncology and Hemato-oncology - Hematology 1
contact_institute: University of Milan - Fondazione IRCCS Ospedale Maggiore Policlinico
